                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-575-18540508 t18540508-575-punishment-2"></join>at the expiration of his Sentence to enter into Recognizance, and find Security to keep the Peace for Twelve Months.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
